        <div> xml:id="Aink102-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">
ituvumatu </p>
          </p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">
And this is that <p/>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Aink102">
            <lg type="edition">
            <l> aṉṉai vāḻivēṇ taṉṉai nammūr </l>
            <l> nīṉiṟap peruṅkaṭaṟ puḷḷi ṉāṉātu</l>
            <l> tuṉpuṟu tuyara nīṅka </l>
            <l> viṉpuṟa vicaikkumavar tērmaṇik kuralē </l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l> Oh Mother! (Listen) with desire Mother! </l>
<l> (Like) the birds (in) our town with a blue-hued, great ocean, </l>
<l> The voice of the chariot bells </l>
<l> </l>            </lg>
        </div>
